summary.name: Atlantic Point Backpackers
summary.tagline: 4-star hostel with outdoor pool, near Cape Town Stadium

address.addressLine: 2 Cavalcade Road, Green Point, Cape Town, Western Cape, 8005

editorial.title: Cape Town
content: Atlantic Point Backpackers is located in Green Point, a neighborhood in Cape Town. Greenmarket Square is worth checking out if shopping is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's popular attractions can visit Two Oceans Aquarium and Kirstenbosch National Botanical Gardens. Looking to enjoy an event or a game while in town? See what's going on at Cape Town Stadium. Practice your golf swing on a nearby course, or enjoy other activities in the great outdoors, such as hiking/biking trails in the area.
